      "name": "Mesh convergence study — FDA generic centrifugal pump",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study (coarse 2.1M, medium 5.4M, fine 11.8M cells) performed at 2.5 L/min / 3500 RPM operating point. Grid convergence index (GCI) computed for velocity magnitude and wall shear stress. Fine-to-medium GCI < 1.8% for all monitored quantities, confirming discretization error is within acceptable bounds for MRL 2.",
