        "description": "GCI computed per Celik et al. (2008) across three mesh levels. Apparent order of convergence p=1.94. Extrapolated relative error < 0.9% for velocity, < 1.6% for WSS. Safety factor Fs=1.25 applied."
      }
    },
    {
