        "type": "UncertaintyQuantification",
        "method": "Comparative sensitivity analysis across turbulence closures",
        "coverageProbability": 0.9,
        "description": "Model-form uncertainty estimated as half the spread between SST k-ω and realizable k-ε predictions. Resulting ±3.6% NIH uncertainty added in quadrature with discretization uncertainty for total combined uncertainty budget."
      }
